---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About - John Milinovich">
  <h1>About me</h1>

  <div class="about-content">
    <p>During UCLA architecture coursework, John Milinovich attended a lecture featuring <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_8DMEHxOLQE">Casey Reas</a> demonstrating Processing.js. This experience prompted a question that continues to guide his work: "when algorithms and humans create together, who's really the artist?"</p>

    <p>This foundational curiosity directed his career path through:</p>

    <ul>
      <li>Early positions at Yahoo and Google</li>
      <li>Founding <a href="https://techcrunch.com/2013/10/16/urx-ads/">URX</a> (later acquired by Pinterest)</li>
      <li>Collaboration with co-founders <a href="https://andrewlook.com/about/index.html">Andrew Look</a> and <a href="https://x.com/nathanael_smith">Nate Smith</a> on GAN experiments</li>
      <li>Launching <a href="https://www.axios.com/2020/04/30/aesthetic-seed-funding-ai-brand-design">Aesthetic</a> to pioneer AI-driven design</li>
      <li>Leadership role at <a href="https://www.nytimes.com/2021/02/15/business/clubhouse.html">Clubhouse</a> in discovery and audio connection</li>
      <li>Current position leading Generative AI Product at <a href="https://www.canva.com/">Canva</a></li>
    </ul>

    <p>He was instrumental in developing <a href="https://www.canva.com/newsroom/news/magic-studio/">Magic Studio</a>, a cross-company initiative recognized among <a href="https://time.com/7094550/canva-magic-studio/">Time's Best Inventions</a> of 2024.</p>

    <p>The narrative arc reflects authentic professional curiosity rather than strategic planning. His diverse background informs contemporary approaches to product development and AI-human collaboration in creative work. He emphasizes simplicity, rapid iteration, and practical engagement with products built.</p>

    <p>Beyond professional endeavors, he explores the world with family. Connect via <a href="https://x.com/jmilinovich">@jmilinovich</a> on X or <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/jmilinovich/">LinkedIn</a>.</p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  h1 {
    font-family: Georgia, 'Times New Roman', serif;
    font-size: clamp(2.4rem, 1vw + 2rem, 3.2rem);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .about-content {
    font-size: clamp(1.7rem, 0.38vw + 1.4rem, 2rem);
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: #333;
  }

  .about-content p {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .about-content ul {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    padding-left: 2rem;
  }

  .about-content li {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .about-content a {
    color: #1a4dc2;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .about-content a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }
</style>
